00:34:04.792 --> 00:34:11.792
world, you are never insecure, you are never
bothered, you have no fear of anyone. You

00:34:13.721 --> 00:34:17.651
do not have to suggest yourself that “you
should not have fear or anything,” you just

00:34:17.651 --> 00:34:25.427
become fearless, there is no nothing like
fear, there's no reaction to any threat or

00:34:25.452 --> 00:34:30.351
anything. Like the gentleman who came here,
just to beat Me now, I was just looking at

00:34:30.351 --> 00:34:35.192
the drama, and the fellow was getting frightened
of Me, he was going backwards, backwards,

00:34:35.192 --> 00:34:41.502
he would not come forward. But you don't develop
any fear of at all about anyone, because you

00:34:41.502 --> 00:34:48.212
are standing on truth, like Christ. At the
time when He was challenged, you must know

00:34:48.212 --> 00:34:55.212
when Mary Magdalene was beaten up, He stood
up. He had nothing to do with the prostitute,

00:34:55.282 --> 00:35:00.282
such a virtuous man, He was virtue personified,
He stood up, He said, “Those who have not

00:35:00.282 --> 00:35:05.772
committed any sin, can throw a stone at Me.”
He was sure nobody can do it because He was

00:35:05.772 --> 00:35:07.012
an authority of virtue.

00:35:07.012 --> 00:35:14.757
I, as I told you, I am just a woman and I
spoke openly with the names of these people

00:35:14.782 --> 00:35:20.552
and told of what they are going to do, and
how they are going to possess you. And people

00:35:20.552 --> 00:35:22.542
came, they were frightened, they said, “What
are You doing?”

00:35:22.542 --> 00:35:29.542
So you get rid of all your fear, but you do
not dominate anyone, you love, in your love

00:35:30.722 --> 00:35:41.316
you are secured. It is not by domination but
the security that you are love, you are compassion.

00:35:41.341 --> 00:35:50.079
And the power of love is the highest of all,
that you stand in complete peace and bliss.

00:35:50.792 --> 00:35:55.431
This happens to you when the central thing
comes up. There are many other things happen,

00:35:55.431 --> 00:36:00.312
